#### 1. 数据准备任务（条件执行）


```json
{
 "task_id": "task_prepare",
 "name": "准备水文数据",
 "tool_name": "prepare_data",
 "type": "simple",
 "parameters": {
 "data_dir": "{DATASET_DIR}/camels_11532500",
 "target_data_scale": "D"
 },
 "conditions": {
 "execute_iterations": "first_only"
 }
}
```

**特性**：
- `execute_iterations: "first_only"` - 只在第一次迭代执行
- 支持的条件值：`"all"`, `"first_only"`, `"skip_first"`, `[1,3,5]`

